==Description==
The '''Dome Fossil''' is a type of [[Fossils|Fossil]].

==Details==
When a '''Dome Fossil''' is placed in the [[Pokémon Day Care]], it hatches into an Kabuto.

==Mine Layout==
The Dome Fossil appears in the Underground as a 4x5 sized object.<br><br>
